Package JurassicPark.Dinosaurs

Class Dinosaur

java.lang.Object
JurassicPark.Dinosaurs.Dinosaur
All Implemented Interfaces:
DinosaurActions, DinosaurStats
Direct Known Subclasses:
Carnivore, Herbivore, Omnivore
public abstract class Dinosaur
extends java.lang.Object
implements DinosaurActions, DinosaurStats
Basic abstract function of actor Dinosaur in simulation, that implements basically every method from implemented interfaces
See Also:
DinosaurStats, DinosaurProperties
